They're all good.

2252
02:13:08,511 --> 02:13:09,979
Good.

2253
02:13:10,012 --> 02:13:13,549
Okay. The navigational hub
has been completely destroyed.

2254
02:13:13,583 --> 02:13:15,151
We don't have
enough life support

2255
02:13:15,184 --> 02:13:16,686
