2258
02:13:20,556 --> 02:13:23,859
Not enough.
But I have a plan.

2259
02:13:23,893 --> 02:13:28,164
We let Gargantua pull us down
close to her horizon.

2260
02:13:28,197 --> 02:13:30,099
